 erinacine A-enriched H. erinaceus mycelia decreased TBARS levels and induced the anti-oxidative enzyme activities of superoxide dismutase, catalase, and glutathione peroxidase. Together, these findings suggest that erinacine A-enriched H. erinaceus mycelia supplement could promote longevity, mediated partly through the induction of endogenous antioxidants enzymes.","tags":["#literature_note"],"author":[{"family":"Li","given":"I.-Chen","literal":""},{"family":"Li","given":"I.-Chen","literal":""},{"family":"Lee","given":"Li-Ya","literal":""},{"family":"Li-Ya","given":"Lee","literal":""},{"family":"Lee","given":"Li-Ya","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Ying-Ju","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Ying-Ju","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Ying-Ju","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Ying-Ju","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Ying-Ju","literal":""},{"family":"Chou","given":"Ming-Yu","literal":""},{"family":"Chou","given":"Ming-Yu","literal":""},{"family":"Wang","given":"Mingfu","literal":""},{"family":"Wang","given":"Ming-Fu","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Wanping","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Wan-Ping","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Wan-Ping","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Yen-Po","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Yen-Po","literal":""},{"family":"Chin-Chu","given":"Chen","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Chin-Chu","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Chin-Chu","literal":""}],"citation-key":"li_erinacine_2019","year":"2019","dateCreated":"2026-03-31","reading-status":"to-read","aliases":["Erinacine A-enriched Hericium erinaceus mycelia promotes longevity in Drosophila melanogaster and aged mice."],"author-links":["[[Author/I.-Chen Li]]","[[Author/I.-Chen Li]]","[[Author/Li-Ya Lee]]","[[Author/Lee Li-Ya]]","[[Author/Li-Ya Lee]]","[[Author/Ying-Ju Chen]]","[[Author/Ying-Ju Chen]]","[[Author/Ying-Ju Chen]]","[[Author/Ying-Ju Chen]]","[[Author/Ying-Ju Chen]]","[[Author/Ming-Yu Chou]]","[[Author/